headline: Capstone Partners Releases 2025 Middle Market Business Owners Research Survey
summary: Capstone Partners, a leading middle market investment banking firm, released its 2025 Middle Market Business Owners Survey Report, with insights from privately-owned companies across the U.S. This report combines Capstone's in-depth middle market knowledge with proprietary data obtained from 401 participating owners of privately-owned, middle market companies.
